=09
A leap year that contains 366 days, with February 29 as an additional day.
<br><br><b>A year is leap year, </b><br>1. if it is <b>divisible by 4</b>, =
then it <b>is leap year</b>, (eg 2020,2016,...)<br>2. if it is <b>divisible=
 by 100</b>, then it <b>isn't leap year</b>, (eg 2100,1900,1800...)<br>3. i=
f it is <b>divisible by 400</b>, then it <b>is leap year</b>, (eg 2000,1600=
,1400...)<br>
<hr>		=09
<b>1. Find Given Year 2000 is Leap Year or not</b><br><br><b>Solution:</b><=
br>
2000 is divisible by 4, but it is also divisible by 100, and it is also div=
isible by 400,<br>So 2000 is a leap year

<br><br><b>2. Leap Years Between the years 1980 and 2004</b><br><br>1 : 198=
